But then again,
there's no rule that

508
00:20:30,878 --> 00:20:32,511
prevents Rem from
killing anyone.

509
00:20:32,544 --> 00:20:33,611
-That's right.

510
00:20:33,644 --> 00:20:35,578
And if you agree to
kill L, it would only

511
00:20:35,611 --> 00:20:37,511
make me love Misa
that much more.

512
00:20:37,544 --> 00:20:39,478
Plus, I'd be grateful to you.

513
00:20:39,511 --> 00:20:43,344
Most importantly, the two of
us will be happy together.

514
00:20:43,378 --> 00:20:46,311
-Rem, I want Light to love me.

515
00:20:46,344 --> 00:20:48,911
And I know we could
be happy together.

516
00:20:48,944 --> 00:20:50,544
It's all I ever wanted.

517
00:21:00,378 --> 00:21:03,111
-That's a shame.

518
00:21:03,144 --> 00:21:03,811
REM: Fine.

519
00:21:03,844 --> 00:21:05,644
-[gasp]

520
00:21:05,678 --> 00:21:07,778
-As you wish, Light Yagami.

521
00:21:07,811 --> 00:21:09,844
But I do not like you.

522
00:21:09,878 --> 00:21:12,278
This will not kill
me, even if it ends up

523
00:21:12,311 --> 00:21:14,644
lengthening your life.

524
00:21:14,678 --> 00:21:16,878
I will kill L for you.

525
00:21:16,911 --> 00:21:18,144
It really makes no difference.

526
00:21:18,178 --> 00:21:20,444
He is just another human to me.

527
00:21:20,478 --> 00:21:22,444
MISA: Hooray!

528
00:21:22,478 --> 00:21:24,378
Oh, Rem, thank you so much.

529
00:21:24,411 --> 00:21:27,578
I knew I could count on you.

530
00:21:27,611 --> 00:21:30,011
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): L will die.

531
00:21:30,044 --> 00:21:31,478
That's all it took.

532
00:21:39,058 --> 00:21:42,291
[theme music]

533
00:22:50,121 --> 00:22:51,421
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): That's right.

534
00:22:51,454 --> 00:22:55,187
Ryuga revealed that he's
L. Therefore, he must die.

535
00:22:55,221 --> 00:22:56,587
The game is over.

536
00:22:56,621 --> 00:22:59,954
[laugh] Tomorrow will
be L's, or at least

537
00:22:59,987 --> 00:23:03,454
Ryuga and Ryuzaki's,
last day alive.

